---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
---

<LegalLayout title="Cookies Policy">
  <p>
    This Cookies Policy explains how Magna Cerámica uses cookies and similar
    technologies on <a href="https://magnaceramica.es">magnaceramica.es</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>1. What are cookies?</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are small text files that a website stores on your device to make it
    work, improve your experience, and provide information to the site owner.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Cookies we use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Strictly necessary cookies:</strong> required for the basic
      functioning of the Website. They do not require consent.</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> help us understand how visitors use
      the site so we can improve it (Google Analytics).</li>
    <li><strong>Third-party cookies:</strong> set by embedded services such as
      Google Maps.</li>
  </ul>

  <table class="cookie-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Cookie</th><th>Provider</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>_ga</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Distinguishes users for traffic analysis</td><td>2 years</td></tr>
      <tr><td>_gid</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Distinguishes users for traffic analysis</td><td>24 hours</td></tr>
      <tr><td>_gat</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Limits the request rate</td><td>1 minute</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Google Maps cookies</td><td>Google Maps</td><td>Enables embedded maps and remembers map preferences</td><td>Varies</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>
    This list reflects the cookies currently expected on this site. It will be
    kept up to date as services (such as the contact form) are added.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Managing cookies</h2>
  <p>
    You can accept, reject, or manage cookies at any time through your browser
    settings. Disabling certain cookies may affect how the Website works. Most
    browsers let you block or delete cookies via their privacy settings.
  </p>

  <h2 id="preferences">4. Cookie preferences</h2>
  <p>
    You can review and update your cookie preferences for this site at any time.
    <span class="placeholder">[The cookie preferences manager will be enabled
    here once the consent tool is integrated.]</span>
  </p>

  <h2>5. More information</h2>
  <p>
    For more details on how we handle your personal data, see our
    <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
